    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in style with this fantastic find! This car is in good condition and has clearly been well-maintained, offering a smooth ride and a clean, comfortable interior. It's a reliable and attractive vehicle that's ready for its next adventure\u2014come see why this solid performer is the perfect choice for you!",
      "price": 35000.0,
