      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably preserved vehicle, currently maintained in showroom condition. This specimen represents a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Every mechanical system has been rigorously vetted to ensure performance that meets the most exacting standards. This is an investment-grade example of automotive excellence, offered for those who demand uncompromising quality.",
      "price": 43500.0,
